Welcome to [B]Project-OS![/B]
Project-OS is Economy Server with an awesome community! Community is always friendly and helpful to everyone. Project-OS is 317/474 based server and got great features. Project-OS was launched on 3/15/2015 and it's officially online now. We are very-very glad to hear all of the suggestions and things what should be added.
We got a lot of things to offer you! All working 20 skills, great PKing system, a lot of bosses in Wilderness and in safezone aswell! There are also Achievemets what you can complete and get rewarded and a lot of more. You are more than welcome to join us and have fun in general. Come and even try it! Project-OS is rapidly growning. We're currently looking for some experienced staff members that are mature and capable for the spot! (no staffhunters). We are putting a lot of time to server and adding a lot of things and fixing everything what is possible.
